    <item>
      <title>距离大选不到一周，勒庞领导的极右翼势力持续崛起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/le-pen-s-far-right-keeps-rising-less-than-a-week-before-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的民意调查显示，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼国民联盟在周日法国提前立法选举第一轮投票前取得了进一步进展，而法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙面临与反对派政府分享权力的可能性越来越大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/le-pen-s-far-right-keeps-rising-less-than-a-week-before-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 07:00:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三菱日联金融集团因客户信息泄露遭日本监管机构处罚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/mufg-is-penalized-by-japan-s-financial-regulator-kyodo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本金融监管机构对三菱日联金融集团的旗舰银行部门及其两家合资企业进行处罚，原因是它们违反了客户保密规则，这可能会对其业务造成进一步打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/mufg-is-penalized-by-japan-s-financial-regulator-kyodo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 03:38:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度 110 亿美元量化共同基金面临监管调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/an-11-billion-fund-manager-says-it-ll-comply-with-india-s-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度快速发展的共同基金行业中，一位新星因涉嫌抢先交易而接受调查，这让人们再次关注到该国监管其蓬勃发展的股票市场的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/an-11-billion-fund-manager-says-it-ll-comply-with-india-s-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 01:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
