      <title>尽管日本加大口头警告力度，日元仍面临压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/japan-s-kanda-says-ready-to-intervene-24-hours-a-day-if-needed-lxs5zzqw</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管日本最高货币官员警告称，当局随时准备在必要时全天 24 小时干预货币市场，但日元周一仍面临压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/japan-s-kanda-says-ready-to-intervene-24-hours-a-day-if-needed-lxs5zzqw</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 23:13:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度长期债券为投资者带来“号角”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/switch-to-india-s-longer-dated-bonds-extends-as-index-date-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明，在印度证券被纳入摩根大通指数之前，印度央行将坚持维持高利率，因此，印度的外国债券投资者正在锁定收益率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/switch-to-india-s-longer-dated-bonds-extends-as-index-date-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
